Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:29.63,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is there no final{\i}\N{\i1}piece to unravel this puzzle?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:36.93,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wander around the search area with dread{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:44.44,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With shaky self-confidence{\i}\N{\i1}facing unyielding damnation,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:48.27,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm still alive, but I can't catch up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:54.45,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to residual images of hidden memories{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:58.66,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let loose dark shame unbounded{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:02.54,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to the ends of this world of kindness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:06.62,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even hopes best forgotten are silenced{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.62,0:01:10.30,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as corruption spreads out before our eyes{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.30,0:01:13.55,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Consign it to darkness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:17.26,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An ego on trial{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.26,0:01:28.40,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a moment of hesitation is seen ecstasy{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kidnapped the Prime Minister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! He played us like a fiddle!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If he got us all together here,\Nand used that opening to attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,then he prepared this carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we went to his\Naid now, we'd be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! There's no need to help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Toki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The Prime Minister is your father, Toki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a little concern for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:01:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,His father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:02:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that's all the more reason, is it not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,On a date. See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.98,0:02:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A date, at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief, what is he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he is thinking along his own lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. He will return.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be more concerned\Nabout what we will do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,About Hitomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...is someone who's never let\Nany of us know what he's thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The cat is talking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes, Yuki has gone Lost, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So you turn into a\Ncat when you go Lost, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's a real hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Miss Sakurakoji,\Nafter taking Hitomi's attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,are you physically all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,For crying out loud, what a fool\Nyou are, exposing yourself to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What do you mean, fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have been killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I just... didn't want anyone else to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That again? How can you be so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't have... anybody dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:30.94,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\bord6\be6\an8}"Episode 8: 'King & Soldier, Child & House'"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, men?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! It'll take more than this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to kill those of us in the Kizakura-gumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Men...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to admit, though,\Nthat long-haired bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He really did use a weird technique.\NJust who was that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi has a special ability\Nover the power of electric shocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Those dead men who showed\Nup at the school yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Their bodies were controlled by Hitomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He also is a former Code: Breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Three years ago,\Nhe disappeared from our sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, the Prime Minister\Nis his former superior, is he not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would he abduct him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He did say revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he have something\Nagainst the Prime Minister?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Even supposing that\NHitomi held some grudge,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,if he wanted to get him back,\Nhe could kill him outright,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,without any kidnapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Some other objective, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What could Hitomi be trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What I {\i1}am{\i} sure of is that he\Nused the police chief and that gang
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to get ready for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The abduction of the Prime Minister
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,may be the culmination of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did Hitomi turn on us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oji...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Number one...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...didn't use to be someone who did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The Number one that\Nwe all know is gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys... You thought a lot of Hitomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi was the Code: Breakers'\Nleader, respected by all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the past may be,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I will burn up all who fall into evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they were once my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sissy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody is here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sissy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right, Toki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You came because you\Nwere worried. I'm delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mean... your memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?\NAnd also, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I'm going\Nshopping with Papa tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I'll save you from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't have... anybody dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is she so insistent?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:07:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It has turned out just as we feared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. No matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura is still our daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! The doctor has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, glad to hear it!\NWe have to go greet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:48.28,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Graduation Ceremony"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor is... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami... What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're looking\Nthrough that album, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That sure takes me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this, here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Finger-lacing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not finger-hooking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Finger-hooking sounds\Npainful, does it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Better to just lace them all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You do this, and by\Ngrasping each other's fingers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it forms a handclasp that\Nallows for an exchange of good cheer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I was little, I would\Nexchange good cheer over and over,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,with my father, my mother,\Nand everyone in the household.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Sakurakoji family tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You sure do love your family, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Both you, and your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, there are no photos of\Nyou as a baby, considering.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you always been so rambunctious,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that they couldn't take any pictures of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's not surprising.\NI was abandoned as a child, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura is not our biological daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She was laid at our\Nmain gate a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a terrible sight,\Nand had blood spattered on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood spatter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but luckily, she was unhurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She was just covered\Nin a massive amount of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,As terrible as she appeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,she must have\Nexperienced something awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That could have been the trigger
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:10:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that made Sakura reject the deaths\Nof others as strongly as she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since that day, we have been\Nanxious that the day would come
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,when Sakura would\Nbe struck by tragedy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanted her to live a happy life, if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it appears\Nthat isn't in the cards for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I don't understand\Nthe kinds of powers you all have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want you to protect Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to rescue her\Nfrom any mishap! I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Number five?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about Hitomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you two were close, huh, Number five?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He just told me to do whatever I felt like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That means he trusted you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, maybe it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi always let things go\Nwithout clearly saying anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,so he was hard to get a handle on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true. Did he say\Nanything to you, Number five?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was little,\NI lost my family in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it tough to be the only survivor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I went through a wild period, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I met Hitomi,\Nhe said something to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"If you've got time to run wild,\Nyou could always just sleep."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi was complaining about being\Nso busy, he had no time to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He was saying he couldn't\Nbelieve that I let my wild behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,cut into my sleeping time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When I heard that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,it made everything getting\Non my nerves seem ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds like Number one, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Number one sure has changed, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He sure has.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I went and fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gone and put everybody out, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What if he were to come to my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm such an idiot! There had\Nto be some other, better way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, how underwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,For a rarebreed like you to get discouraged,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,like normal people do, is so disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not discouraged...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason this whole business\Nstarted is because I went Lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it wasn't enough\Nthat I feel small about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,why should you have to be\Ntroubled by it, too, Miss Sakurakoji?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't you act so stuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if you go getting discouraged,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:12:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to make fools out of those
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,who believe in and follow you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy's got it right, Miss Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Sakura, injuries\Nlike these are no big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd be treating us like strangers
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,if you didn't bring home your school pals
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,when they're being chased by bad guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time that bastard shows up,\Nwe'll turn the tables on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry to have\Nlet you face that kind of danger
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,while we were here with you, Miss Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're really glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! If I face them like this,\Nit will just make them worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on me! I'm the one\Nwho needs more training!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Letting myself be caught by\Nthat scrawny man is a huge screw-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisuke, train me harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's more like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We used to be like that once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. All centered around Hitomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure wish we could all\Nfight like we did then again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oji, do you believe in Hitomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to. There must be some reason for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right. Number one is\Nacting like a different person now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Something happened to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph, what nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in what\Nmight have happened to Hitomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just pissed off, and I won't\Nrest until I've slugged him one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The great Toki will knock some\Nsense back into that Hitomi jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,With that much settled,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,let's all split up and search\Nfor Hitomi and the Prime Minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "Let's go-go time!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, there's nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Eden takes care of things left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I didn't think anything\Nwas left here in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no leads here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami, why did Hitomi\Nabduct the Prime Minister?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know him going back,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,there must be something\Nthat comes to mind, is there not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami, were you and Hitomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- C'mon batter! C'mon, c'mon!\N- All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a seat, Miss Kanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So the rarebreed's\Npower is greater than imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you not tell me in advance
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that Miss Sakurakoji was a rarebreed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you were once under Hitomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanted to avoid the risk\Nof any information being leaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of your relationship with Hitomi,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,discrepancies in our contacts arose,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and we were also mistaken about Ogami
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:17:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to immolate Sakurakoji Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, since she is a rarebreed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,we did not think there was any\Nconcern about Ogami harming her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you suspected me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Part of our job was to supervise you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to make sure you weren't\Nsecretly communicating with Hitomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought Hitomi would\Ntry to make contact with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but that was a miscalculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I am... Ogami Rei's agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to do with Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then are you able to dispose of Hitomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I can. I'll stake\Nmy pride as an agent on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The world that Hitomi seeks...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The world that the Prime Minister seeks...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you come up with any leads on Hitomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use. I can't find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like killing the\Npolice chief and that {\i1}yakuza{\i} bunch
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is now working against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Prime Minister's home?\NAre you working to salvage it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Heike,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,you're being awfully negligent,\Nconsidering, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You had to know that by getting\Nall the Code: Breakers together,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it would leave the area around\Nthe Prime Minister shorthanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not the one who called you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It was your arbitrary\Ndecision that sent in Yuki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you doubt me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're surprisingly sharp-witted, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's Illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:18:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the start of Hitomi's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Number five!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Another explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnificent! Such is the\Nshadow special ability for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A black guardian angel,\Nthe only one among the Code: Breakers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that can defend lives against all attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this, Heike?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you. Hitomi's plan has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And with that, Oji,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to need you to leave the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,However excellent you may be at protecting,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,in this situation, you will\Nbe unable to avoid my attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Number five!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that... a fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami, what happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Heike!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Sakurakoji, Ogami was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami was?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}are{\i} being targeted by Hitomi, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a secret base.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:21:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! A Code: Breaker\Nsecret base?! This is so exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is dark. Are there no lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Prime Minister Fujiwara!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here, Heike?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,As promised, I have\Nbrought you the rarebreed, Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you will allow me to join you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Heike?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I have decided to turn on the Code: Breakers,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.65,0:21:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and side with Hitomi, instead.\NYou are a gift to that end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be a good hostage, Miss Sakurakoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.83,0:22:01.55,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day, you, too, will know{\i}\N{\i1}where that white crow is heading{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:07.22,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We fly through the brilliant city,{\i}\N{\i1}unnoticed by all around{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.60,0:22:21.73,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looking only for a reason to live{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:27.15,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ashamed of our hollow selves{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.15,0:22:31.91,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should we just laugh and go along{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.91,0:22:37.58,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with the rules the world has decided on?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.58,0:22:42.34,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stripped bare, following{\i}\N{\i1}wherever our instincts lead{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:46.38,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to the truth from{\i}\N{\i1}which we've averted our eyes{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.38,0:22:51.01,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Verdicts handed down for no one's sake{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.01,0:22:55.85,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cast off the dark robes and get on your feet{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.85,0:23:00.56,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pure white wishes become our wings{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.56,0:23:05.28,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shake off your hesitations now, and fly high{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:13.74,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have no fear; the answers{\i}\N{\i1}lie beyond the darkness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullets of sorrow, sneering light,\Nand a dark resolution laid bare.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.89,0:23:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time,\N"Code: Breaker" episode 9, "Stopped Time."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.81,0:23:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue flame, light up\Nthe darkness of betrayal!
